#

Balsamic Glazed Chicken with Garlic Mashed Cauliflower

40 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freelow-carb

Cuisine:

AmericanItalian

Course:

mainside

Tags:

quickhealthycomfort food

Description

Tender chicken coated in a sweet and tangy balsamic glaze, served with creamy garlic mashed cauliflower for a healthy twist.

Ingredients

  • chicken breasts: 2 pieces
  • balsamic vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • honey: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • cauliflower: 1 head
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • chives (optional): for garnish
